Hi Russ,
You have the power wire to the idiot lights hooked to #30 contant power 
instead of to where the #15 connection for the coil, cut off solinoid, & 
electric choke should be connected and are then only powered when the key is 
turned to the ignition or run positions.
Eric&Barb

